2026-05-11T05:43:33.8208485Z 23        Exact alarm permissions. We request both so reminders fire reliably
2026-05-11T05:43:33.8209196Z 24        across Android versions:
2026-05-11T05:43:33.8210197Z 25          - SCHEDULE_EXACT_ALARM: required on Android 12 (API 31-32); the
2026-05-11T05:43:33.8211106Z 26            user must toggle it on via Settings. We prompt for this in
2026-05-11T05:43:33.8211931Z 27            MainActivity when canScheduleExactAlarms() returns false.
2026-05-11T05:43:33.8212762Z 28          - USE_EXACT_ALARM: auto-granted on Android 13+ (API 33+) for
2026-05-11T05:43:33.8213605Z 29            calendar/reminder/timer-style apps, so no prompt is needed.
2026-05-11T05:43:33.8214452Z 30        Without USE_EXACT_ALARM the app was silently falling back to
2026-05-11T05:43:33.8215277Z 31        inexact alarms on Android 13+, which Samsung (and other OEMs)
